  "comment": "The Prometheus is an extremely versatile system that can provide up to 40 feet of flame on command.  It can be mounted to a truss or be secured down to a flat surface using standard screws and the provided mount. The burner is water and weather resistant. With a central rack mount controller capable of handling the DMX control of multiple burner heads, or an optional single head controller, this system provides a reliable and cost-effective option for companies who need a rugged and sleek flame system that exceeds industry standards. The Prometheus is listed by ARL testing lab to the NFPA 160 standard.",
